<%= render :partial => "/shared_templates/email_header" %>
<p>Dear <%=h get_user_name_or_pseudo(@user) %>,</p>

<p>You receive this email because you are a moderator or admin of an organism.</p>

<p>A comment has been posted</p>

<p>Comment's text:<br />
  <%= h @comment.text %></p>

<p>You can eventually:</p>

<p>Suspend the comment (in case it's not respecting the rules):<br />
  <%=h @url_suspend %></p>

<p>You can see the comment in its context:<br />
  <%= @parent_object_url %></p>

<p>Regards.</p>
<%= render :partial => "/shared_templates/email_footer" %>